+{"id":"bd-2i1","title":"Close TUI history mode visual/interaction parity","description":"Close remaining TUI history mode parity gaps. Needs richer git/correlation-rich history UI, deeper commit detail view, and full timeline interaction parity with legacy bv.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-27T04:03:05.821261152Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-27T04:52:19.557857814Z","closed_at":"2026-02-27T04:52:19.557829531Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
+{"id":"bd-2i6","title":"Conformance: large-dataset stress-test fixtures and adversarial edge cases","description":"Background: large/adversarial fixture coverage is a critical parity confidence lever and already partially underway.\\nWork: expand and harden stress fixtures (size, shape, pathological dependencies, malformed metadata) and keep fixture intent documented.\\nAcceptance: fixture suite reproduces known edge conditions and catches regression classes that minimal fixtures miss.\\nTesting/logging: fixture generation and validation steps must emit detailed metadata and provenance logs.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-27T21:53:17.916549894Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-27T22:27:07.883270470Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2i6","depends_on_id":"bd-33w.6","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-05T00:07:49Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-2i6","depends_on_id":"bd-33w.6.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-05T00:07:49Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
