+{"id":"bd-33w.2.2","title":"Port recipe and script workflow surfaces: --robot-recipes, --recipe, --emit-script, feedback controls","description":"Background: operators need recipe-driven prioritization and script emission for agent workflows.\\nWork: implement recipe listing/application, script generation with format/limit controls, and feedback tuning commands (accept/ignore/show/reset).\\nAcceptance: script outputs deterministic, recipe behaviors match documented semantics, feedback visibly influences recommendation weights.\\nTesting/logging: fixture tests for recipe outputs and emitted scripts; explicit logs showing applied weight deltas.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-02-27T22:25:56.320261275Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-05T00:39:11.777805168Z","closed_at":"2026-03-05T00:39:11.777783387Z","close_reason":"Implemented recipe/script/feedback CLI surfaces: --robot-recipes, --recipe, --emit-script/script-format/script-limit, --feedback-show/accept/ignore/reset. Backend logic in analysis/recipe.rs was already complete; added pub mod export, CLI flags, and main.rs dispatch. All 9 recipe tests pass.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["automation","recipes","robot"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-33w.2.2","depends_on_id":"bd-33w.2","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-05T00:07:49Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-33w.2.2","depends_on_id":"bd-33w.2.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-05T00:07:49Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
